name: Jersey
description: Apparel worn by soccer players during matches. Usually represents a specific team or national team.

name: Goalkeeper Gear
description: Equipment specifically designed for goalkeepers such as gloves for better grip and protection.

name: Soccer Shoes
description: Footwear designed for soccer players optimized for various playing styles and positions.

name: Socks
description: Specialized socks worn by soccer players for added comfort and support during matches.

name: Soccer Ball
description: The ball used in soccer matches typically featuring various designs for different tournaments or leagues.

name: Training Equipment
description: Gear used for training purposes focusing on improving skills and physical attributes.

name: Shorts
description: Apparel worn by soccer players during matches specifically focusing on lower body clothing.

name: Soccer Technique Books
description: Books or guides aimed at helping soccer players improve their skills and techniques.

name: Soccer Bags
description: Bags designed to carry soccer equipment clothing~~ and accessories.
